-- Peugeot Citroen Strengthens Its Partnership With Dongfeng Motors in China
-- B y   M a r t h e   F o u r c a d e
-- 2010-09-21T06:41:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/peugeot-citroen-strengthens-its-partnership-with-dongfeng-motors-in-china.html
PSA Peugeot Citroen agreed to
strenghten its partnership with Dongfeng Motors in China. The
companies plan to introduce 12 new cars in five years, build a
third plant and gain 5 percent of the local market by 2015,
Peugeot said in an e-mailed statement today. 